itemDescription: English clergyman and writer; archdeacon of East Riding

wikipedia_page.main: Robert Isaac Wilberforce (19 December 1802 – 3 February 1857) was an English clergyman and writer.

response: *Agnes Frances Everilda, daughter of the first marriage, on 16 June 1832 married Robert Isaac Wilberforce, who succeeded her father as archdeacon of the East Riding.
